You can configure chromium with NixOS the standard way:

\<syntaxhighlight\> nixpkgs.config = {

       firefox = {
        jre = false;
        enableGoogleTalkPlugin = true;
        enableAdobeFlash = true;
       };

       chromium = {
        jre = false;
        enableGoogleTalkPlugin = true;
        enableAdobeFlash = true;
       };

     };

\</syntaxhighlight\>

and then install \*chromiumWrapper\*

